patchNoteDetails:
#### Pokémon

### Metagross
Metagross was grossly overtuned. These changes bring Magnet Rise to lower uptime and damage while bring Gyroball down in damage as well. Metagross Unite bugs are being fixed as well.
###### Gyro Ball \[NERFED\]
**Damage**:
Ratio: 250% Atk -> 215% Atk
Slider: 10 - > 10
Base: 650 -> 560
&nbsp;

###### Magnet Rise \[NERFED\]
**Cooldown** increased: 7s -> 9s
&nbsp;
**Movement Speed** decreased: 80% -> 60%
&nbsp;
**Movement Speed decay** decreased: 16% -> 15%
&nbsp;
**Movement Speed duration** decreased: 5s -> 4s
&nbsp;
**Damage**:
Ratio: 230% Atk -> 140% Atk
Slider: 5 - > 5
Base: 250 -> 250
&nbsp;

###### Unite Move: Compute and Crush
**Unstoppable** added
&nbsp;
Fixed an bug where the Unite move gauge would recover to 90% even though the move was activated.
&nbsp;
Fixed an issue where an invisible wall would remain even after the wall that had been generated had timed out automatically.
&nbsp;
